Parameter Optimizer — Profit vs Threshold / Rolling Window / Stop Loss
=======================================================================
For each market cap, finds ticker CSVs in Downloads, fetches price +
sentiment data once, sweeps the chosen parameter, and saves one profit
chart per market cap.

Requirements:
    pip install curl_cffi pandas scipy pytz matplotlib
"""

